dc_title_s: Land Use St. Croix County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data layer represents land use for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'St_Croix_LandUse_2018.gdb'. [The proposed land use classification identified during community planning activities and sometimes defined at the parcel level, but typically proposed land use units are larger than the parcel.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://sccgis-scccdd.opendata.arcgis.com/
